snippet.title: KenJu - Unreleased Atomiswave game now on Dreamcast!
snippet.description:
Footage of KenJu, the unreleased Atomiswave fighting game now playable on Dreamcast thanks to megavolt85! Check out the Dreamcast-Talk form here: https://www.dreamcast-talk.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=5&t=13982

Read our article on this game here:https://www.thedreamcastjunkyard.co.uk/2021/02/lost-atomiswave-fighter-kenju-ported-to.html

Recorded on a DCHDMI with a GDEMU installed.
